 FROM "warehouse"."dbt"."fct_batches" as batches

SELECT
    case_activities.id,
    case_activities.endtime,
    case_activities.completed,
    case_activities.terminated,
    case_activities.createtime,
    case_activities.caseactivityid,

    case_activities.caseactivityname,
    case_activities.caseactivitytype,
    case_activities.casedefinitionid,
    case_activities.durationinmillis,
    cases.businessKey,
    cases.id as case_id,
    cases.caseDefinitionName
FROM "warehouse"."dbt"."fct_case_activities" as case_activities
LEFT JOIN "warehouse"."dbt"."fct_cases" as cases
ON ( case_activities.caseinstanceid = cases.id )

    superCaseInstanceId,
    superProcessInstanceId,
    active,
    completed,
    terminated,
    closed
FROM "warehouse"."dbt"."fct_cases" as processes

SELECT
    id,
    decisionDefinitionId,

SELECT
    activities.id,
    activities.starttime,
    activities.endtime,
    EXTRACT(EPOCH FROM (activities.endtime - activities.starttime)) as duration_seconds,
    activities.activityid,
    activities.activityname,
    activities.activitytype,
    processes.id as process_id,
    processes.businesskey,
    processes.processdefinitionname,
    processes.processdefinitionkey
FROM "warehouse"."dbt"."fct_activities" as activities
LEFT JOIN "warehouse"."dbt"."fct_processes" as processes
ON ( activities.processinstanceid = processes.id )

SELECT
    processes.id,
    processes.starttime,
    processes.endtime,
    EXTRACT(EPOCH FROM (processes.endtime - processes.starttime)) as duration_seconds,
    processes.state,
    processes.processdefinitionname,
    processes.processdefinitionkey,
    processes.businesskey
FROM "warehouse"."dbt"."fct_processes" as processes

SELECT
    tasks.id, 
    tasks.processInstanceId, 
    tasks.caseInstanceId, 
    tasks.activityInstanceId, 
    tasks.name, 
    tasks.description, 
    tasks.owner, 
    tasks.assignee, 
    tasks.startTime, 
    tasks.endTime,
    tasks.duration,
    EXTRACT(EPOCH FROM (tasks.endTime - tasks.startTime)) as duration_seconds,
    processes.processdefinitionname,
    processes.businesskey as process_businesskey,
    processes.id as process_id,
    cases.caseDefinitionName,
    cases.businesskey as case_businesskey,
    cases.id as case_id,
    activities.activityname,
    activities.activityid as activityid
FROM "warehouse"."dbt"."fct_tasks" as tasks
LEFT JOIN "warehouse"."dbt"."fct_processes" as processes
ON ( tasks.processInstanceId = processes.id )
LEFT JOIN "warehouse"."dbt"."fct_cases" as cases
ON ( tasks.caseInstanceId = cases.id )
LEFT JOIN "warehouse"."dbt"."fct_activities" as activities
ON ( tasks.activityInstanceId = activities.id )

select

    activityid,
    processdefinitionkey 
from "warehouse"."dbt"."dim_activities"
group by activityid,processdefinitionkey order by count asc

    count(*),
    activityid 
from "warehouse"."dbt"."dim_activities"
where endtime is NULL group by activityid order by count desc

SELECT 
    id, 
    processdefinitionkey,
    businesskey,
    interval '1 second' * duration_seconds as duration
FROM 
    "warehouse"."dbt"."dim_processes"
WHERE duration_seconds is not null order by duration_seconds desc limit 20

SELECT 
    processdefinitionkey,count(*) 
FROM 
    "warehouse"."dbt"."dim_processes"
 WHERE endtime is null group by processdefinitionkey order by count asc
